  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House",
    "asOf": "2020-05-22",
    "date": "2020-06-17T18:46:12Z",
    "text": "Service Assurance Act of 2020\n\nThis bill exempts nonprofit organizations from liability for any act or omission relating to harm arising from exposure to, or infection by, the coronavirus (i.e., the virus that causes COVID-19) during the COVID-19 public health emergency. However, this\u00a0exemption does not apply with respect to\u00a0acts or omissions that constitute willful or criminal misconduct, gross negligence, reckless misconduct, or conscious and flagrant indifference to the rights or safety of the individual harmed."
  },
